descriptionNullable:
The data in the dataset lists all the best selling products on amazon in the category clothing and accessories. The columns in the DataFrame include:

Ranking: The ranking or position of the product in the list of best-selling apparel products.

Title: The title or name of the apparel product.

Reviews: The number of reviews or feedback received for the product.

Ratings: The rating or average customer rating for the product.
title: Amazon's Bestsellers in Clothing & Accessories
